With best regards,
Ville Nordberg

We are looking for a backend developer, with strong .net experience. This developer will manage and build the backend of a fitness and travel platform, where endpoints are used to securely serve content from our database. Additionally, this person will manage and integrate with various 3rd party APIs to retrieve content, e.g. for hotel information, or manage authentication.

We are fully in the cloud. Azure and CI/CD expertise would be a plus - while there is no frontend work required, it would be beneficial to be close to frontend for integration and improvement of the service.
